      "id": "PopularPost8106",
      "post_content": "The Medallions were and still are quite amazing. Effectively moxen for those of us who can't afford moxes. The green one wasn't as good as the others, simply because green uses alot of 1 mana cards and has little need for a ramp of this kind (cards like Earthcraft and even Llanowar Elf is more useful, usually). But its still a great utility card.",
