    {
      "id": "PopularPost298636",
      "post_content": "This card is actually really awesome. My friend ran a Green Wurm artifact deck and had one of these on turn two. On turn Three he played 3 [Nature's Lore](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nature's Lore)s and still having all 2 of his lands untapped to play a [Copper Myr](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Copper Myr). Next turn he played a [Symbiotic Wurm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Symbiotic Wurm). To say the least this card works pretty darn well with green mana ramp since it can lower the costs of creatures and the ramp spells themselves. 4.75/5 for solidness.  ",
      "posted_by": "BobbertZhubert",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost298636\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">This card is actually really awesome. My friend ran a Green Wurm artifact deck and had one of these on turn two. On turn Three he played 3 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Nature's Lore\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nature's Lore\">Nature's Lore</a>s and still having all 2 of his lands untapped to play a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Copper Myr\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Copper Myr\">Copper Myr</a>. Next turn he played a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Symbiotic Wurm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Symbiotic Wurm\">Symbiotic Wurm</a>. To say the least this card works pretty darn well with green mana ramp since it can lower the costs of creatures and the ramp spells themselves. 4.75/5 for solidness.<br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '298636'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy92124\">BobbertZhubert</span>\r\n                                (2/7/2013 12:48:32 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<d