    {
      "id": "PopularPost350220",
      "post_content": "I don't know. I think the \"Green doesn't need Artifacts for mana\" is a bad argument.   \n  \nThese are some cards I think are fair:   \n  \n[Sol Ring](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sol Ring)  \n[Primeval Titan](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Primeval Titan) (though I do wish it said \"Basic\", or listed \"Mountain or Forest\", or qualified in some way to prevent it getting some certain troublesome nonbasic lands).  \n[Armageddon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Armageddon)  \n[Worldfire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Worldfire)  \n[Balance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Balance)  \n  \nAlthough its true they can all be abused, they also all are easy and obvious enough to metagame around. I think that if Green wants to be the color of \"Happy-Go-Lucky-Look-it-Me! I Have Billions of Land!\", then it is equally righteous and just to allow some powerful Land Destroyers to be floating around to deflate it if it gets degenerate. LD should be treated like Counterspells: every individual card in the two categories, even [Strip Mine](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Strip Mine) and [Force of Will](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Force of Will), is actually \\*BY NATURE\\* fair, because they stop \"Pow... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost350220\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">I don't know. I think the \"Green doesn't need Artifacts for mana\" is a bad argument. <br/><br/>These are some cards I think are fair: <br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sol Ring\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sol Ring\">Sol Ring</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Primeval Titan\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Primeval Titan\">Primeval Titan</a> (though I do wish it said \"Basic\", or listed \"Mountain or Forest\", or qualified in some way to prevent it getting some certain troublesome nonbasic lands).<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Armageddon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Armageddon\">Armageddon</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Worldfire\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Worldfire\">Worldfire</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Balance\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Balance\">Balance</a><br/><br/>Although its true they can all be abused, they also all are easy and obvious enough to metagame around. I think that if Green wants to be the color of \"Happy-Go-Lucky-Look-it-Me! I Have Billions of Land!\", then it is equally righteous and just to allow some powerful Land Destroyers to be floating around to deflate it if it gets degenerate. LD should be treated like Counterspells: every individual card in the two categories, even <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Strip Mine\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Strip Mine\">Strip Mine</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Force of Will\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Force of Will\">Force of Will</a>, is actually *BY NATURE* fair, because they stop \"Pow... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 350220)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '350220'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46041\">DarthParallax</span>\r\n                                (11/6/2013 4:11:59 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: le